<L>__{exterior a road in virginia day.}
<A>__{paul is chained by the ankles to forty five other men. he hands are shackled. in his mouth, an iron bit... the men are being led by white guards with rifles. camera follows them under a burning sun as they approach; a trench. one thousand feet long. five feet deep. five feet wide. camera tilts down to reveal, within the trench; wooden boxes, with scrap limber roofs and a door of bars fitted on them like a cage that opens up to a wall of red dirt stretching two feet above the top of the bars themselves.}
